  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个评论状态流转图，核心是评论从创建到最终处理的完整生命周期。首先，评论创建后应该先进入一个待审核状态，我称之为Pending。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Create Comment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Pending是入口状态。那从Pending可以有哪些出口？审核通过和拒绝应该是主要分支吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Pending可以Approve变成Approved状态，也可以Reject变成Rejected状态。另外用户应该能随时Delete，所以Pending和Approved、Rejected都应该能走向Deleted。Deleted是终态，数据会归档到Redis缓存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
        "Approve",
        "Reject",
        "Delete",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，主干结构有了。我注意到你提到Deleted指向Redis，这个用虚线还是实线？另外Pending内部好像还有细节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Deleted",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Pending"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Pending内部需要细化：评论先进入AwaitingModeration子状态，等待负载均衡器分配审核任务。Approved内部也有子结构——通过后评论变为Visible，用户可以Edit，编辑后回到Visible，形成循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Approved",
        "Visible",
        "Edited",
        "Update"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Visible和Edited的双向流转我记下了。那Rejected状态呢？也需要类似的内部结构吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rejected",
        "Visible",
        "Edited"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Rejected下评论先变为Hidden，然后可以Add Rejection Reason进入WithReason状态，最终流向LoadBalancer做后续处理。另外需要在各状态旁加注释说明，比如Pending旁边注明\"Comments start in Pending state and await moderation\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rejected",
        "Hidden",
        "WithReason",
        "Add Rejection Reason",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Pending"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。我检查了整体结构：EtcdCluster作为起点，经过Pending及其子状态AwaitingModeration，分支到Approved（含Visible/Edited循环）或Rejected（含Hidden/WithReason），各状态均可Delete至Redis，注释也已添加在四个主状态右侧。",
